SUMMARY:Family square dance
DTSTAMP:20260317T050008Z
DTSTART:20260321T023000Z
DESCRIPTION:Ballard (5 miles NW)\n\nThe $10 Square Dance has a live band an
	d a caller to instruct beginners at Urban Family Brewing\, 1103 NW 52nd St
	. in Seattle. Children younger than age 18 are free.\n\nhttps://urbanfamil
	ybrewing.com/product/square-dance/\n\nFrom Events12 Seattle
URL:https://urbanfamilybrewing.com/product/square-dance/
LOCATION:https://www.google.com/maps/search/?api=1&query=Urban%20Family%20B
	rewing%2C%201103%20NW%2052nd%20St%2C%20Seattle%2C%20WA%2098107
