UID:sSe1pB2PU9IEE-sqTJGOc
SUMMARY:Endless Opportunities: Volunteer Birthday Dreams
DTSTAMP:20260317T050008Z
DTSTART:20260323T200000Z
DESCRIPTION:Join us in bringing joy\, dignity\, and celebration to children
	 experiencing homelessness through this Birthday Dreams service project. B
	irthday Dreams is a nonprofit organization dedicated to bringing hope\, jo
	y\, and a sense of self-worth to homeless children with the gift of a birt
	hday party\, partnering with more than 80 shelters across the Puget Sound 
	region to ensure every child feels loved and remembered on their special d
	ay. We’ll come together to assemble goody bags and curate other birthday i
	tems that are delivered to local shelters and families. These items help c
	reate a complete birthday experience—from party favors and treats to thoug
	htful supplies that make each child’s celebration feel magical and meaning
	ful.\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/endless-opportunitie
	s-volunteer-birthday-dreams/18305982/2026-03-23T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - All 
	Events
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/endless-opportunities-vol
	unteer-birthday-dreams/18305982/2026-03-23T00
LOCATION:Stroum Jewish Community Center\, 3801 East Mercer Way\, Mercer Isl
	and\, WA
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:seatoday-all
CATEGORIES:SEAtoday - All Events
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT2H
